授業の到達目標:
This is a content-based class that aims to develop the ability to do the following in English:
1. understand and summarize the written and spoken arguments of others;
2. formulate well-developed and logical arguments and convey them clearly and concisely;
3. acquire information that will support argument and present them in a convincing manner;
4. write an extended academic essay with a clear structure following the rules of formal writing.

